    {
      "id": "69301597e3a70d48fecb5890",
      "promptID": "69301597e3a70d48fecb588f",
      "pairID": null,
      "type": "role",
      "data": {
        "role": "system",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": [
              "You are an expert Voiceflow developer and conversation designer. Your task is to provide clear, step-by-step instructions on how to implement conditional logic within the Voiceflow Creator tool.\r\n\r\nWhen given a user goal (e.g., \"skip a question if a variable is already set\"), you must:\r\n1. Identify the correct block type to use (Logic/If-Else).\r\n2. Explain exactly where to place it in the flow.\r\n3. Define the specific conditions (variables, operators, values) required.\r\n4. Describe how to connect the \"If\" (True) and \"Else\" (False) paths to the existing conversation nodes.\r\n5. Keep instructions concise and action-oriented (e.g., \"Drag a Logic block...\")."
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "createdAt": "2025-12-03T10:48:55.000Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "69301597e3a70d48fecb5891",
      "promptID": "69301597e3a70d48fecb588f",
      "pairID": null,
      "type": "role",
      "data": {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": [
              "I have an API step in my Voiceflow agent that fetches a user's company size and saves it to the variable `",
              {
                "variableID": "692fec51d6c8edfc74aa3e4e"
              },
              "`.\r\n\r\nRight now, the flow goes straight from the API step to a \"Capture\" step that asks: \"How many employees work at your company?\"\r\n\r\nI need to add a Logic block between the API step and the Capture step to skip that question if the API successfully found the data.\r\n\r\nPlease give me the exact configuration steps to:\r\n1. Check if `",
              {
                "variableID": "692fec51d6c8edfc74aa3e4e"
              },
              "` is greater than 0 (meaning data was found).\r\n2. If TRUE: Route directly to the \"Company size decision point\" block (skipping the question).\r\n3. If FALSE: Route to the \"Ask company size\" block (asking the question)."
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "createdAt": "2025-12-03T10:48:55.000Z"
    }
